  "html": "<h3 style=\"text-align:center;\">Experience Letter</h3>\n<p>This is to certify that <b>{{ doc.employee_name }}</b> was employed with us as a \n<b>{{ doc.designation }}</b> from <b>{{ doc.date_of_joining }}</b> \nto <b>{{ doc.relieving_date }}</b>.</p>\n\n<p>During this period, {{ doc.employee_name }} has performed duties sincerely and was found to be \nprofessional and dedicated.</p>\n\n<p>We wish them success in their future career.</p>\n\n<br><br>\n<p><b>Authorized Signatory</b></p>\n",
